title: Raymundo Reveals A Long Kept Secret + Lunchbox Catches Eddie Lying + Bobby Plays The Disney Songs Game!
itunes:title: Raymundo Reveals A Long Kept Secret + Lunchbox Catches Eddie Lying + Bobby Plays The Disney Songs Game!
description:
Raymundo shares a secret he’s been keeping from his wife for a year now. Lunchbox talks about what he's going to do when he wins the lottery tonight. Lunchbox says Eddie has been lying to the entire show. Plus, Raymundo plays a song from a famous Disney movie and the crew has to try and guess the movie!
